{"tid":1145805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院既分享平台 出咗條宣傳片講一帶一路既陷阱","createTime":"2019-05-09T00:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T01:58:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e4b6dbcde0f0d8cf3754940c554534b5072e99","tid":1145805,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:45:28.000Z","msg":"(殘體）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DpgIvWoL8zI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDpgIvWoL8zI&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfr6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=1301f40b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DpgIvWoL8zI</a><br />\n<br />\n2019 五月 01<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前中國正在擴展其一帶一路倡議。世界各國應該對其以往投資工程的表現多加註意和考察。<br />\n<br />\n中國承諾提供數十億美元用於基礎設施建設的貸款和經濟發展，但中國一帶一路涉及的風險和代價包括 過於沈重的債務、環境問題、喪失對戰略資產的控制等，對 接受國造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n中國的一帶一路倡議要求恢復和擴大將中國與世界連接的著名絲綢之路（Silk Road）貿易通道。<br />\n<br />\n美國則通過透明、自由和公平的貿易協議提供更好的方案 。<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯（Pence）在出席2018年亞太經合組織峰會（APEC Summit）期間表示，「我們不會讓我們的合作夥伴淹滅在債務的海洋中。我們不會脅迫或損害你們的獨立。」<br />\n<br />\n[編者安：地圖不具備權威性。]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://share.america.gov/zh-hans/dont-get-caught-in-chinas-belt-and-road-debt-trap-video/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.america.gov%2Fzh-hans%2Fdont-get-caught-in-chinas-belt-and-road-debt-trap-video%2F&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfr6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=548faa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://share.america.gov/zh-hans/dont-get-caught-in-chinas-belt-and-road-debt-trap-video/</a>"},{"pid":"531ebca6d8dec8dc556d4dd5eac1d8ce87e0f6cb","tid":1145805,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:47:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4c8093827ce30ead718cf617bb10752fc8c0f40d","tid":1145805,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ae833aff8002db0b576ab1891c86fcab04a593","tid":1145805,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci